66
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:36,540
Not yet, Auntie.

67
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:39,000
I can take care of myself.

68
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,230
Fine.

69
00:05:40,230 --> 00:05:43,500
If you ever need anything, come and talk to me.

70
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:45,010
Don't feel awkward asking.

71
00:05:45,010 --> 00:05:46,684
And come to our place and dine with us.

72
00:05:46,684 --> 00:05:49,024
It would be more cheerful if we have more people at home.

73
00:05:49,690 --> 00:05:51,250
Thank you, Auntie.

74
00:05:51,250 --> 00:05:54,593
You guys enjoy it. I'll head out and buy some fruit.

75
00:05:55,490 --> 00:05:57,190
Enjoy.

76
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:59,340
Don't forget your wallet again.

77
