00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:33,065
 My mom told me that my grandma looked so much better today.

180
00:13:33,065 --> 00:13:37,340
 The doctor said that she would be out of ICU soon.

181
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:43,935
 Another thing is that I'm going to stay at Zhou Siyue's place tomorrow.

182
00:13:43,935 --> 00:13:49,200
 Is this the irresistible force of fate?

183
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:55,980
 The door of fate suddenly opened at the end of this summer.

184
00:14:19,130 --> 00:14:20,630
Morning.

185
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:23,940
Have you packed everything?

186
00:14:27,130 --> 00:14:30,190
You have just one case?

187
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:31,866
My place is close by.

188
00:14:31,866 --> 00:14:34,570
I can always come back and pick up things.

189
00:14:37,157 --> 00:14:38,957
Let's go.

190
00:14:39,763 --> 00:14:42,740
- Where are we going?
 - Shopping.

191
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:48,910
This doesn't look bad.

192
00:14:51,631 --> 00:14:54,050
And this is not bad either.

193
00:14:57,710 --> 00:15:00,030
Let's get some juice.

194
00:15:07,233 --> 00:15:09,423
And one instant noodle.

195
00:15:14,673 --> 00:15:17,233
We need some shampoo.

196
00:15:18,459 --> 00:15:20,359
One second.

197
00:15:21,654 --> 00:15:26,470
Do you think I need to use anti-hair loss shampoo?

198
00:15:33,130 --> 00:15:34,670
I still don't need it.

199
00:15:34,670 --> 00:15:37,450
I have a lot of hair to lose.

200
00:15:37,450 --> 00:15:39,490
I don't know which one you would prefer.

201
00:15:39,490 --> 00:15:41,320
Let's buy a few types and try them.

202
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:44,950
Let's just take the most basic one.

203
00:15:49,860 --> 00:15:52,210
We still need shower gel.

204
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:57,270
I have one at home. I can just bring it.

205
00:15:57,793 --> 00:15:59,593
Okay.

206
00:15:59,593 --> 00:16:01,470
You are pretty economical.

207
00:16:01,470 --> 00:16:03,306
That's because you waste too much money.

208
00:16:03,306 --> 00:16:06,790
Let me lead the way. Give it to me. I'll handle it.

209
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:08,230
Hey.

210
00:16:11,180 --> 00:16:13,480
I'll carry it.

211
00:16:14,692 --> 00:16:16,153
Lead the way.

212
00:16:16,153 --> 00:16:18,830
Let's head towards the stationery area.

213
00:16:20,919 --> 00:16:23,073
We are in the stationery area now.

214
00:16:23,073 --> 00:16:24,980
What are we buying?

215
00:16:24,980 --> 00:16:27,860
Let's see. This is so cute.

216
00:16:27,860 --> 00:16:30,000
It's childish.

217
00:16:43,130 --> 00:16:45,440
It looks fancy, but it's expensive and hard to use.

218
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:48,110
When have you ever seen me using that?

219
00:16:48,110 --> 00:16:50,380
This is amazing.

220
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:54,640
Are you a kid?

221
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:56,760
Even my brother is not using that anymore.

222
00:16:56,760 --> 00:16:58,370
What does your brother know?

223
00:16:58,370 --> 00:17:00,893
Here. One for each of us.

224
00:17:00,893 --> 00:17:02,380
Fine.

225
00:17:02,380 --> 00:17:04,522
Let it compensate for your childhood.

226
00:17:04,522 --> 00:17:06,422
Come on.

227
00:17:06,422 --> 00:17:07,996
What else?

228
00:17:08,739 --> 00:17:12,000
Ding Xian. Zhou Siyue.

229
00:17:12,830 --> 00:17:14,830
Keke!

230
00:17:16,900 --> 00:17:20,490
What are you two doing together?

231
00:17:20,490 --> 00:17:23,010
This is my new errand boy.

232
00:17:23,010 --> 00:17:26,090
Fine. Whatever you say.

233
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:33,559
What are you two doing together?

234
00:17:33,559 --> 00:17:38,700
Wh-Why can't we hang out?

235
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:40,280
Let's put that aside.

236
00:17:40,280 --> 00:17:43,340
She told me that you are so good at pool.

237
00:17:43,340 --> 00:17:45,858
Why don't we have a go at it sometime?

238
00:17:46,970 --> 00:17:49,550
Can you try to find out some worthy information?

239
00:17:51,853 --> 00:17:53,653
What are you doing?

240
00:17:53,653 --> 00:17:56,300
Don't interrupt when girls are talking.

241
00:17:56,950 --> 00:17:59,210
What's going on with you two?

242
00:17:59,210 --> 00:18:01,350
Nothing.

243
00:18:01,350 --> 00:18:03,680
Stop lying and tell me the truth.

244
00:18:06,300 --> 00:18:08,300
It's just that...

245
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:12,210
You are living with Zhou Siyue?

246
00:18:12,820 --> 00:18:14,540
What?

247
00:18:14,540 --> 00:18:16,750
 You didn't even tell me something so important!

248
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:19,540
 I had to hear it from Keke.

249
00:18:19,540 --> 00:18:22,640
No. It's not like that.

250
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:26,260
I'm just staying at his place for a few days.

251
00:18:26,260 --> 00:18:28,485
 Xianxian, can I come in?

252
00:18:28,485 --> 00:18:31,130
Auntie, please come in.

253
00:18:31,130 --> 00:18:34,490
 Xianxian, I got you a new towel.

254
00:18:36,393 --> 00:18:37,880
Is this room serving you well?

255
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:41,700
It's a little hasty, so I just arranged it quickly.

256
00:18:41,700 --> 00:18:44,330
Tell me if you need anything.

257
00:18:44,330 --> 00:18:46,190
It's okay. I have everything here.

258
00:18:46,190 --> 00:18:48,280
It makes me happy to see you.

259
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:51,370
You are nice and sensitive.

260
00:18:51,370 --> 00:18:55,190
I have always wanted to have a daughter like you.

261
00:18:56,130 --> 00:18:58,680
 I forgot to put away the photos.

262
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:01,580
This was taken when Siyue was young.

263
00:19:02,610 --> 00:19:05,120
Auntie, isn't this in Keshan?

264
00:19:05,120 --> 00:19:08,840
Yes. That's your place.

265
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:11,243
That's the first time Siyue ever went to Keshan.

266
00:19:11,243 --> 00:19:13,730
There happened to be a flood.

267
00:19:13,730 --> 00:19:17,490
His grandpa sent him to your place.

268
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:22,660
He cried for the whole day after he got back, saying that he was never going to Keshan again.

269
00:19:22,660 --> 00:19:25,500
I think he was terrified by the flood.

270
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:27,520
This one is interesting.

271
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:30,340
That's a photo of Siyue dressed up like a girl when he was young.

272
00:19:30,340 --> 00:19:33,180
- This photo...
 - Mom!

273
00:19:33,900 --> 00:19:35,998
Why did you take that photo out again?

274
00:19:35,998 --> 00:19:38,286
How come you are everywhere?

275
00:19:38,286 --> 00:19:40,530
I'm having a chat with Xianxian.

276
00:19:40,530 --> 00:19:44,730
Xianxian, if he ever bothers you, tell me.

277
00:19:44,730 --> 00:19:46,950
I'll make him pay.

278
00:19:47,912 --> 00:19:49,090
All right.

279
00:19:49,090 --> 00:19:52,040
But he's actually nice, Auntie.

280
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:55,710
Take a shower before going to bed.

281
00:19:55,710 --> 00:19:58,950
Siyue, help Xianxian to unpack.

282
00:19:58,950 --> 00:20:00,981
Thank you, Auntie.

283
00:20:08,660 --> 00:20:11,260
You look unusual...

284
00:20:13,370 --> 00:20:16,060
in that photo.

285
00:20:20,900 --> 00:20:25,190
My mom was obsessed with giving me weird looks back then.

286
00:20:25,190 --> 00:20:27,670
Who would remember stories from childhood?

287
00:20:27,670 --> 00:20:30,910
Take a shower and sleep.

288
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:35,820
 Ding Xian! Hello?

289
00:20:35,820 --> 00:20:37,340
 Hello, Ding Xian.

290
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:39,140
Hello?

291
00:20:39,140 --> 00:20:41,860
And you are saying nothing happened! Now, you are taking a shower.

292
00:20:41,860 --> 00:20:45,085
- No. It's not like that.
  - I don't care.

293
00:20:45,085 --> 00:20:48,833
The girls are having a meeting tomorrow. You have to be there. See you.

294
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:09,090
Why didn't you lock the door?

295
00:21:10,673 --> 00:21:12,473
You should continue.

296
00:21:13,460 --> 00:21:15,780
Where is the hairdryer?

297
00:21:20,149 --> 00:21:22,149
Mom!

298
00:21:22,149 --> 00:21:24,330
Where is the hairdryer?

299
00:21:24,330 --> 00:21:29,060
 It's in... the cabinet under the sink.

300
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:31,350
 Look carefully.

301
00:22:04,413 --> 00:22:06,303
Ding Xian.

302
00:22:07,176 --> 00:22:09,626
We are about to be late.

303
00:22:13,780 --> 00:22:15,950
Are you still sleeping?

304
00:22:21,259 --> 00:22:25,330
 The second set of national gymnastics for middle school students.

305
00:22:25,330 --> 00:22:28,660
 The era is calling.

306
00:22:33,210 --> 00:22:35,450
 Ready! Go!

307
00:22:39,759 --> 00:22:41,916
What's your problem, Zhou Siyue?

308
00:22:41,916 --> 00:22:43,516
Hurry up!

309
00:22:56,447 --> 00:22:58,741
Why are you riding a bike today?

310
00:22:58,741 --> 00:23:00,093
You are so slow.

311
00:23:00,093 --> 00:23:01,664
I don't want to be late.

312
00:23:01,664 --> 00:23:03,380
It's not like I begged you to wait for me.

313
00:23:03,380 --> 00:23:06,026
You could have gone if you were in a hurry.

314
00:23:06,026 --> 00:23:08,070
I have really spoiled you.

315
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:09,540
Hey.

316
00:23:09,580 --> 00:23:13,740
If you don't want to be late, you can beg me to give you a ride.

317
00:23:13,740 --> 00:23:15,210
I don't need that.

318
00:23:15,210 --> 00:23:16,963
Sleepyhead!

319
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:19,515
Childish!

320
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:35,610

321
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:38,460
Morning, Shadi.

322
00:23:38,460 --> 00:23:40,760
Morning.

323
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:42,783
I've seen this before.

324
00:23:42,783 --> 00:23:47,190
How's life with your dream guy in the next room?

325
00:23:47,190 --> 00:23:50,180
What are you talking about? What dream guy?

326
00:23:50,180 --> 00:23:52,540
He's a psycho!

327
00:23:52,540 --> 00:23:54,940
You should know when to take a win.

328
00:23:54,940 --> 00:23:57,711
You have to tell me everything today.

329
00:23:58,460 --> 00:24:02,636
Living in the same apartment is not as nice as you imagined.

330
00:24:02,636 --> 00:24:03,838
Think about it.

331
00:24:03,838 --> 00:24:11,036
Would you like to see Song Ziqi at every corner every day?

332
00:24:11,036 --> 00:24:13,016
Now that you mention it,

333
00:24:13,016 --> 00:24:16,230
we did live together for a while when we were young.

334
00:24:16,230 --> 00:24:17,620
Tell me about it.

335
00:24:17,620 --> 00:24:19,420
Here's the story.

336
00:24:19,420 --> 00:24:22,420
Song Ziqi has always liked to run away from home when he was young.

337
00:24:22,420 --> 00:24:25,090
Back then, our families were close.

338
00:24:25,090 --> 00:24:28,300
He liked to come and stay at our place. He'd sleep on the floor of my room.

339
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:33,780
And when he sleeps, he snores, grinds his teeth, and farts.

340
00:24:33,780 --> 00:24:35,380
And that's not the most outrageous thing.

341
00:24:35,380 --> 00:24:37,941
- You know what the most outrageous is?
 - What?

342
00:24:37,941 --> 00:24:40,210
Every time... I mean, every time!

343
00:24:40,210 --> 00:24:42,300
After our nap in the middle of the day,

344
00:24:42,300 --> 00:24:47,400
he was always on the bed and I was on the floor.

345
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:49,753
How could he do that?

346
00:24:49,753 --> 00:24:54,380
In comparison, my life is pretty good.

347
00:25:15,930 --> 00:25:19,270

348
00:25:21,686 --> 00:25:23,386
Thank you.

349
00:25:26,893 --> 00:25:28,540
What else?

350
00:25:28,600 --> 00:25:31,700
Didn't you talk about things during the night?

351
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:35,200
What would we say?

352
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:37,437
We were both exhausted.

353
00:25:37,437 --> 00:25:38,820
That's boring.

354
00:25:38,820 --> 00:25:40,220
Boring.

355
00:25:40,700 --> 00:25:44,940
Although, if we think about it, this is like "Full House."

356
00:25:44,940 --> 00:25:48,562
There are still a lot of days ahead.

357
00:25:48,562 --> 00:25:51,500
You should cut down on teen dramas.

358
00:25:51,500 --> 00:25:54,380
On the other hand, I think the shorter the distance,

359
00:25:54,380 --> 00:25:55,660
the easier your illusion about each other vanishes.

360
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:57,010
Like you would know.

361
00:25:57,010 --> 00:25:58,920
It's not like you've lived with anyone else.

362
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:00,320
You...

363
00:26:01,010 --> 00:26:02,930
I'll let you do the talking.

364
00:26:05,490 --> 00:26:08,180
I don't know what to say.

365
00:26:08,180 --> 00:26:12,680
Anyway, I am happy.

366
00:26:13,610 --> 00:26:16,260
What a fickle girl.

367
00:26:27,580 --> 00:26:31,602
Master Zhou, how are things going?

368
00:26:31,602 --> 00:26:34,746
A guy and a girl in the same house.

369
00:26:36,730 --> 00:26:38,500
That's complete nonsense.

370
00:26:38,500 --> 00:26:40,730
Where did the "in the same house" come from?

371
00:26:40,730 --> 00:26:42,697
Was I wrong?

372
00:26:42,697 --> 00:26:44,710
Little Monster is at least

373
00:26:44,710 --> 00:26:48,240
a young, beautiful, and neat girl.

374
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:49,330
A girl.

375
00:26:49,330 --> 00:26:51,620
What about me? Why would I take him in?

376
00:26:51,620 --> 00:26:54,920
A guy. And I had to pay for his family dispute.

377
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:59,796
What? Why are you looking at me like that?

378
00:27:00,250 --> 00:27:03,830
When are you planning to go back this time?

379
00:27:04,300 --> 00:27:07,013
Don't blame me for saying this. Your dad has outdone himself this time.

380
00:27:07,013 --> 00:27:09,533
This is not the first time he has done this.

381
00:27:09,533 --> 00:27:13,890
But it is a new record, right?

382
00:27:13,890 --> 00:27:15,380
Think about it.

383
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:17,970
Even if your dad doesn't want to find you since he's angry,

384
00:27:17,970 --> 00:27:21,477
your mom would inevitably feel a little worried. Right?

385
00:27:29,420 --> 00:27:31,950
Come on, let's go play games.

386
00:27:42,100 --> 00:27:45,959
My mom went to play Mahjong. Let's make do with this.

387
00:27:53,860 --> 00:27:58,190
Do you usually have dinner by yourself?

388
00:27:59,540 --> 00:28:04,410
It is joyous to have someone to dine with.

389
00:28:04,410 --> 00:28:05,610
Not bad.

390
00:28:05,610 --> 00:28:08,812
Really? Then you should cherish the time we have.

391
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:11,130
There's nothing to worry about.

392
00:28:11,130 --> 00:28:13,490
I could always be a freeloader at your place.

393
00:28:13,490 --> 00:28:15,545
In your dreams!

394
00:28:21,163 --> 00:28:23,143
It's a little salty, right?

395
00:28:23,840 --> 00:28:26,390
My mom doesn't cook.

396
00:28:26,390 --> 00:28:27,920
How about this?

397
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:30,594
Let's go have dinner outside.

398
00:28:30,594 --> 00:28:33,250
No. I think it's nice.

399
00:28:33,250 --> 00:28:36,872
Besides, home cooking is always the better choice.

400
00:28:38,580 --> 00:28:42,680
Enjoy. And do the dishes later.

401
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:45,420
What?

402
00:28:45,420 --> 00:28:48,090
I never charged you for the tutoring.

403
00:28:48,090 --> 00:28:50,497
You should make it up to me.

404
00:28:52,220 --> 00:28:55,818
All right. I'll do the dishes, Master Zhou.

405
00:29:10,580 --> 00:29:12,853
You have prepared fruit, too.

406
00:29:16,332 --> 00:29:19,137
If you are not watching TV, can I?

407
00:29:19,137 --> 00:29:20,910
Sure.

408
00:29:23,540 --> 00:29:26,110
Where did you put the remote control?

409
00:29:30,130 --> 00:29:32,100
Did you hide it?

410
00:29:32,900 --> 00:29:35,830
Why would I hide it?

411
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:40,180
It's not here.

412
00:29:40,180 --> 00:29:41,660
Stand up and let me see.

413
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:44,786
I didn't hide it. Don't touch me!

414
00:29:44,786 --> 00:29:47,062
I saw it. You did hide it. It's here.

415
00:29:47,062 --> 00:29:49,553
You are still trying to talk your way out of this.

416
00:29:49,553 --> 00:29:51,980
Have you finished your homework yet?

417
00:29:51,980 --> 00:29:55,587
I have. Just let me watch it.

418
00:29:55,587 --> 00:29:57,573
All right.

419
00:30:00,210 --> 00:30:03,282
Come. If you can grab it, you get to watch it.

420
00:30:07,300 --> 00:30:11,300
Zhou Siyue! Stop pushing me!

421
00:30:11,300 --> 00:30:13,690
Even if I am pushing you, so what?

422
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:22,426
I've been fighting with my brother for the remote control at home for years. That counts for something.

423
00:30:25,220 --> 00:30:27,328
You strike hard!

424
00:30:27,328 --> 00:30:31,277
It's because you always get to watch TV in peace.

425
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:39,316
Look at you.

426
00:30:39,316 --> 00:30:43,346
You are just like my brother when he can't get the remote control.

427
00:30:56,070 --> 00:30:57,160
Hey.

428
00:30:58,980 --> 00:31:01,660
Did you use the website I gave you last time?

429
00:31:01,660 --> 00:31:03,360
I did.

430
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:08,200
And I like it a lot. Thank you.

431
00:31:10,460 --> 00:31:15,940
I'm glad. My effort was not in vain.

432
00:31:16,610 --> 00:31:21,413
If you need a computer, you can use mine. The password is six zeros.

433
00:31:21,940 --> 00:31:23,540
Really?

434
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:28,100
You can have the remote control. Let me borrow your computer.

435
00:31:29,780 --> 00:31:32,130
Don't stay up too late. We need to get up early tomorrow.

436
00:31:32,130 --> 00:31:33,930
 Got it!

437
00:31:38,151 --> 00:31:42,831

438
00:31:46,526 --> 00:31:48,380
I told you to sleep earlier.

439
00:31:48,380 --> 00:31:51,420
Look at how you slept during classes.

440
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:53,020
I did go to sleep early.

441
00:31:53,020 --> 00:31:55,140
 I was playing Mahjong with Zheng's wife.

442
00:31:55,140 --> 00:31:57,994
 He said that Zheng was at home, tutoring his son.

443
00:31:57,994 --> 00:32:00,160
 Zhou Zongtang, you lied to me.

444
00:32:00,160 --> 00:32:01,809
 Can you knock it off?

445
00:32:01,809 --> 00:32:03,570
 The kids are about to get back.

446
00:32:03,570 --> 00:32:05,640
 I said it a lot of times, and you just won't believe it.

447
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:07,080
 Zheng was there.

448
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:08,830
 He left after a phone call.

449
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:10,780
 Jiang was there with me the whole time. You can ask him about it.

450
00:32:10,780 --> 00:32:13,280
 Don't treat me like I'm clueless. Jiang is on your side.

451
00:32:13,280 --> 00:32:15,152
 He lied for you before.

452
00:32:15,152 --> 00:32:16,960
 I don't trust him.

453
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:19,950
 Zhou Zongtang, tell me the truth.

454
00:32:19,950 --> 00:32:21,640
 Do you have another woman out there?

455
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:25,000
 What are you talking about? I can't do this with you.

456
00:32:29,730 --> 00:32:31,630
Xianxian is here.

457
00:32:31,630 --> 00:32:33,940
Why didn't you say that you were home?

458
00:32:33,940 --> 00:32:37,491
You didn't tell me you were back either.

459
00:32:37,491 --> 00:32:38,840
You must be hungry now.

460
00:32:38,840 --> 00:32:41,070
Jinyun, the kids are back.

461
00:32:41,070 --> 00:32:42,910
I'm going to cook now.

462
00:32:50,100 --> 00:32:54,300
Siyue and Xianxian are back. I'll go help your dad.

463
00:33:20,540 --> 00:33:22,240
Come in!

464
00:33:38,133 --> 00:33:40,293
Do you have another question?

465
00:33:40,293 --> 00:33:42,090
I'll go help you after I finish this.

466
00:33:42,090 --> 00:33:44,896
It's okay. You should focus on what you are doing.

467
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:48,060
You are preparing for the Academic Olympiad, right?

468
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:50,530
I just wanted to check up on you.

469
00:33:54,780 --> 00:33:57,080
My room is a bit messy.

470
00:33:57,080 --> 00:33:58,740
Sit.

471
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:20,140
Have you read all these books?

472
00:34:26,633 --> 00:34:28,660
I just want to tell you

473
00:34:28,660 --> 00:34:31,260
that I will never tell another soul about what I heard today.

474
00:34:31,260 --> 00:34:34,052
I promise. I swear.

475
00:34:36,660 --> 00:34:39,646
All couples fight.

476
00:34:39,646 --> 00:34:42,276
Don't be sad.

477
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:49,080
What?

478
00:34:49,080 --> 00:34:53,570
Did you just realize that my family is not as harmonious as you thought,

479
00:34:53,570 --> 00:34:55,993
so you feel things are fair now?

480
00:34:55,993 --> 00:34:57,466
No.

481
00:34:57,466 --> 00:34:59,166
Really?

482
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:07,203
Maybe a little.

483
00:35:09,709 --> 00:35:12,436
But I'm not gloating.

484
00:35:15,220 --> 00:35:17,295
It's okay.

485
00:35:19,190 --> 00:35:23,190
My mom doesn't work.

486
00:35:23,190 --> 00:35:26,560
So, she's all focused on my dad.

487
00:35:26,560 --> 00:35:28,580
You know that my dad is busy at work.

488
00:35:28,580 --> 00:35:31,160
He never had the time to stay with my mom.

489
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:35,693
That's why my mom is always suspicious and making scenes.

490
00:35:35,693 --> 00:35:37,909
I'm used to it.

491
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:45,738
Besides, look at my mom.

492
00:35:45,738 --> 00:35:48,220
She grew up in a well-off family.

493
00:35:48,220 --> 00:35:51,960
That's why she thinks everyone is doing everything for her sake.

494
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:54,500
She never holds a grudge.

495
00:35:54,500 --> 00:36:00,155
She will forget a lot of things in a few days.

496
00:36:01,700 --> 00:36:06,390
But I do remember all the things

497
00:36:06,390 --> 00:36:08,760
that my mom has gone through.

498
00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:17,280
What?

499
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:20,970
Did you just realize that I'm also not as nice as you thought?

500
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:25,728
No. Why would I think that?

501
00:36:26,940 --> 00:36:29,040
Stop lying to me.

502
00:36:32,810 --> 00:36:35,256
I think you are great.

503
00:36:38,580 --> 00:36:41,207
We are just 17.

504
00:36:41,207 --> 00:36:45,059
There will be a lot of trouble and confusion.

505
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:49,390
No one is perfect.

506
00:36:50,260 --> 00:36:54,040
So, don't pressure yourself.

507
00:37:02,470 --> 00:37:05,000
My dad and I are different.

508
00:37:05,530 --> 00:37:09,080
I will never let people around me feel bad.

509
00:37:22,919 --> 00:37:27,019
You drink it. Sleep tight afterward.

510
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:53,803
 When Shadi and Keke asked me that day,

511
00:37:53,803 --> 00:37:56,563
 I didn't know the answer.

512
00:37:56,563 --> 00:37:58,870
 But I think,

513
00:37:58,870 --> 00:38:03,560
 for me, maybe there is no fantasy or disillusionment.

514
00:38:03,560 --> 00:38:06,020
 Sometimes he's sweet

515
00:38:06,020 --> 00:38:08,766
 and sometimes annoying.

516
00:38:09,610 --> 00:38:12,260
 He can be vulnerable occasionally.

517
00:38:12,260 --> 00:38:15,820
 All of those things about him just makes me happy.

518
00:38:15,820 --> 00:38:21,500
 Because right now, he's real, both in my heart

519
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:23,560
 and in front of me.

520
00:38:23,560 --> 00:38:25,870
 He won't disappear.

521
00:38:32,140 --> 00:38:33,920
What are you smiling about?

522
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:38,582
We have been getting along pretty well lately.

523
00:38:38,582 --> 00:38:41,736
And I know a lot of his secrets.

524
00:38:41,736 --> 00:38:44,680
What secrets? Let me hear them.

525
00:38:44,680 --> 00:38:48,570
I can't. I promised to keep those secrets for him.

526
00:38:48,570 --> 00:38:50,780
You are such a spoilsport.

527
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:52,580
But I would never have guessed

528
00:38:52,580 --> 00:38:55,090
that Master Zhou who has always been perfect

529
00:38:55,090 --> 00:38:58,560
would have something that you can use.

530
00:39:06,530 --> 00:39:09,450
Have you heard about what happened to He Xingwen?

531
00:39:12,420 --> 00:39:15,660
I think his dad had an accident at the construction site.

532
00:39:24,660 --> 00:39:26,460
Stand up!

533
00:39:27,660 --> 00:39:30,660
Hello, Teacher.

534
00:39:30,660 --> 00:39:32,360
Please take a seat.

535
00:39:36,740 --> 00:39:42,150
Some of you may have heard that there has been an accident in He Xingwen's home.

536
00:39:42,150 --> 00:39:44,660
Although this is a donation of your own will,

537
00:39:44,660 --> 00:39:47,780
I still hope you would lend a helping hand

538
00:39:47,780 --> 00:39:52,742
so that He Xingwen and his family can get through this hard time.

539
